Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, Fey Blade mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,why are we flying all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it was my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, would you at least tell me where we are headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:58.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an area called Sekikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Like its name,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like a coffin made from stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, it was a typical village,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was about twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,before that incident occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:19.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, they all suddenly disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The humans in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean... a mysterious disappearance, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of it remains unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:38.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But, like the villagers, the people sent to investigate the place vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone gave up on the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and instead put the area under lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Last Demon Tool: The Weaponless Kid's Impossible Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:20.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This wall looks terrible, almost as if the builders were trying to desperately cover something up before anyone discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what Shibusen is trying to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think the mood here is getting kinda scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop saying those things right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!{\alphaHFF} No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:39.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way!{\alphaHFF} No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:39.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! No way!{\alphaHFF} No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:39.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm going in there, absolutely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters or whatever, you know I can't deal with those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was even written in my fortune-telling ticket that I should never get involved with those things again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be going in alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's a virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,or a chemical substance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,or a monster's doings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,or even a totally different cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:09.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is that every human that's gone in has never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing what the cause is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply couldn't bring both of you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That would just be too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but you do have a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:29.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is also the reason honorable father sent me, not someone else, on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be dangerous to go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:38.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the recent series of actions taken by Shibusen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,are based on the belief that they would lead them to the Demon Tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't come out in forty minutes, I want you to go back to Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about going in to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:57.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Postponing the final battle with the Kishin for something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall see with my own eyes, just how great a tool it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Connection with thirteenth squadron lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:10.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteenth and seventeenth squadron, remain in contact and attack the enemies in area 34!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty bad out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think we should give some orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If we knew what those "orders" would be, then we wouldn't be having a headache here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I find any kind of orders better than doing nothing and watching them suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:32.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be fortunate if those impulsive orders didn't make the situation worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop looking at me with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, it'd be great to be free like you two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, sometimes would think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:51.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,how great it'd be if I could do whatever I wanted, the way I wanted, and wherever I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,His words sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the only ones feeling irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If only his soul wasn't bound to Death City...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,he would've been the first to make it to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the forgotten village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt any odd changes since I've come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing abnormal about the air, so it's normal that I can't sense any form of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm sure there's something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:19.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the inside of an ancient ruin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~ supervisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if you would just call me BJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:35.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Supervisor, it's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm not your supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Supervisor, we've prepared some coffee for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm not your supervisor, let's have some of that coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig~ in~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure is a big key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Obtaining a key so easily in a huge ancient ruin such as this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:32.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there should be no doubt that this is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:01.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We both know that you're running hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you know where you're heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:30.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you should really think about the consequences before you take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I did ask you what you wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:41.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't get to Medusa by just running around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my Soul Perception ability to seek out Medusa's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa has her Soul Protect on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's different for Professor Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Crona and Marie-sensei are also looking for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can sense their soul, I'll use them to get to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Stein, who even Shibusen couldn't locate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and Crona and Marie who went after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:18.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we're trying to find three people that could be anywhere in the world, without any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even begin to imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure it'll turn out alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, somehow it'll turn out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I need your help, Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the security system that's protecting the Demon Tool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the qualifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have what it takes to wield the Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey clown,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it also you who attacked the villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow humans to come into this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:24.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lay their hands on the Demon Tool shall receive no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're the one responsible for what happened twenty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the resting place for the last Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The last Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:41.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Those humans foolishly dug out this ruin twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:45.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They were delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,All criminals shall be purged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,shall be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I'd let you eat me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,With that huge body of his, he'll never reach me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What a simplistic design.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,See, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left now is to meet up with Liz and Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There was another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid sure is slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No matter how long he takes, h-he'll definitely make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think it's best if we went and got him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you k-k-kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would go into a scary place like that?! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we both go in and get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear a word I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:49.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did. You were telling me the story about Mr. Pig, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:58.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen when others are talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear that! I didn't hear that! I didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, they're persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Symmetrical!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Not symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Symmetrical!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Not symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Symmetri-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Not symmetrical!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:44.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's undoubtedly the true symmetr-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They just can't see the beauty of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit more... If I can reach that building...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back the Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun, we've come to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've conquered your fear of monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you destroy all the buildings around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay for what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back! Give it back!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,These enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks bad! They're too stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:48.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Resonance stable. Noise at 2.7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Needles... fully charged with soul wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Feedback in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Firin'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me finish this with beautiful symmetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:43.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to activate auto-recovery... System not responding...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:50.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damaged received: 92%. Activation time remaining: 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:19:00.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, you who defeated this guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from the voice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:13.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you, do you have the will to use the Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For those who do not possess the will, there shall be no glory...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Only destruction awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:30.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:37.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has the right to say that what we're doing now isn't a sin that can't be atoned for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:42.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can tell for sure, that Shibusen will never use the Demon Tools for evil deeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Demon Tool of this mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's hard to believe that it was protected by such a security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This could just be the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to use it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,then things would be much simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:24.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those words you heard bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:38.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I'm now wondering if giving this Demon Tool to honorable father is the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me ask you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For those who do not possess the will, there shall be no glory...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only destruction awaits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:05.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you'll be the last man standing.
